#~ msgctxt "Name"
#~ msgid "GOCR"
#~ msgstr "GOCR"

#~ msgctxt "Comment"
#~ msgid ""
#~ "<emphasis>GOCR</emphasis> (sometimes known as <emphasis>JOCR</emphasis>) "
#~ "is an open source OCR engine, originally started by Joerg&nbsp;"
#~ "Schulenburg and now with a team of active developers.<nl/><nl/>See <link "
#~ "url=\"http://jocr.sourceforge.net\">jocr.sourceforge.net</link> for more "
#~ "information on GOCR."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<emphasis>GOCR</emphasis> (včasih znan kot <emphasis>JOCR</emphasis>) je "
#~ "odprtokodni razpoznavalnik znakov (OCR), ki ga je sprva začel Joerg&nbsp;"
#~ "Schulenburg zdaj skupaj z ekipo aktivnih razvijalcev.<nl/><nl/>Oglejte si "
#~ "<link url=\"http://jocr.sourceforge.net\">jocr.sourceforge.net</link> za "
#~ "več informacij o GOCR."

#~ msgctxt "Name"
#~ msgid "OCRAD"
#~ msgstr "OCRAD"

#~ msgctxt "Comment"
#~ msgid ""
#~ "<emphasis>OCRAD</emphasis> is a free software OCR engine by Antonio&nbsp;"
#~ "Diaz, part of the GNU&nbsp;Project.<nl/><nl/>Images for OCR should be "
#~ "scanned in black/white (lineart) mode. Best results are achieved if the "
#~ "characters are at least 20&nbsp;pixels high. Problems may arise, as "
#~ "usual, with very bold or very light or broken characters, or with merged "
#~ "character groups.<nl/><nl/>See <link url=\"http://www.gnu.org/software/"
#~ "ocrad/ocrad.html\">www.gnu.org/software/ocrad/ocrad.html</link> for more "
#~ "information on OCRAD."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<emphasis>OCRAD</emphasis> je prosti program za OCR avtorja Antonio Diaz, "
#~ "ki je del projekta GNU.<nl/><nl/>Slike za OCR je treba skenirati v črno-"
#~ "belem (linijskem) načinu. Najboljše rezultate dosežemo, če so znaki "
#~ "visoki vsaj 20 slikovnih pik. Ponavadi se lahko pojavijo težave z zelo "
#~ "krepkimi ali zelo tankimi ali polomljenimi znaki ali z združenimi "
#~ "skupinami znakov.<nl/><nl/>Oglejte si <link url=\"http://www.gnu.org/"
#~ "software/ocrad/ocrad.html\">www.gnu.org/software/ocrad/ocrad.html</link> "
#~ "za več informacij o OCRAD."

#~ msgctxt "Name"
#~ msgid "Tesseract"
#~ msgstr "Tesseract"

#~ msgctxt "Comment"
#~ msgid ""
#~ "<emphasis>Tesseract</emphasis> is a free software OCR engine, originally "
#~ "developed at HP&nbsp;Labs and now sponsored by Google. It supports "
#~ "multiple languages and scripts (including right-to-left text) and page "
#~ "layout analysis.<nl/><nl/>The best results are achieved if scanned "
#~ "characters are at least 20&nbsp;pixels high. Problems may arise with "
#~ "excessively skewed or rotated images, or if dark borders are present.<nl/"
#~ "><nl/>See <link url=\"https://github.com/tesseract-ocr/tesseract\">github."
#~ "com/tesseract-ocr/tesseract</link> for more information on Tesseract."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<emphasis>Tesseract</emphasis> je prosta programska oprema za OCR, ki je "
#~ "bila prvotno razvita v HP Labs, zdaj pa ga sponzorira Google. Podpira več "
#~ "jezikov in skript (vključno z besedilom od desne proti levi) in analizo "
#~ "postavitve strani.<nl/><nl/>Najboljši rezultate dosežemo, če so skenirani "
#~ "znaki visoki najmanj 20 pik. Težave lahko nastanejo pri pretirano "
#~ "nagnjenem oz. zasukanih slikah ali če so prisotne temne obrobe.<nl/><nl/"
#~ ">Glejte <link url=\"https://github.com/tesseract-ocr/tesseract\">github."
#~ "com/tesseract-ocr/tesseract</link> za več informacij o Tesseractu."

